            ‚öôÔ∏è System Prompt (Advanced - Optional)
          </summary>
          <div class="p-4 border-t bg-gray-50">
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">
              Edit the AI system prompt to customize content generation behavior. Leave default for RSOC v3.5 compliance.
            </p>
            <textarea 
